@NODE N6 "Look customization"
@{B}Program settings@{UB}

The Sudominator settings window contains following gadgets:

@{B}Sudoku Foreground Color@{UB} sets the color used for drawing sudoku grid and digits.

@{B}Selected Field Brightness@{UB} sets the amount of brightening or darkening (negative
values) when drawing background of the active sudoku field.

The sudoku field uses Input List frame and background. It also uses default big
font. These items are configured via MUI preferences.
@ENDNODE
